{"lineNumber":53706,"originalJapaneseLine":"「かなみ、何ボケッとしてる！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Kanami, what are you spacing out for!"},

{"lineNumber":53707,"originalJapaneseLine":"　力ずくでいくぞ","translatedEnglishLine":"We're going in with force."},

{"lineNumber":53708,"originalJapaneseLine":"「う、うん！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Y-yeah!\""},

{"lineNumber":53709,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっぶなー。あぁそーーぉ？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That was close. Oh yeah?!"},

{"lineNumber":53710,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ほな、すっ飛んでもらうで","translatedEnglishLine":"Then, you'll be sent flying."},

{"lineNumber":53711,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちっ、それがあったか……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Tch, so that's what you've got...\""},

{"lineNumber":53712,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ほい、リターン……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Here, return...\""},

{"lineNumber":53713,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふっ……魔法ブレイク！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hah... Magic Break!\""},

{"lineNumber":53714,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おっ……お、おおぉぉ？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh... ohhh?"},

{"lineNumber":53715,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なんや、リターンが……","translatedEnglishLine":"What's this, a return..."},

{"lineNumber":53716,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふっ、ふっははははははは！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hah, hahahaha!"},

{"lineNumber":53717,"originalJapaneseLine":"　異次元とゲートを繋ぐことができるなら、","translatedEnglishLine":"If you can connect an interdimensional gate,"},

{"lineNumber":53718,"originalJapaneseLine":"　その接続を切ることもまた可能","translatedEnglishLine":"then severing that connection is also possible."},

{"lineNumber":53719,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……ぶっつけ本番だったが、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...It was all impromptu, but,"},

{"lineNumber":53720,"originalJapaneseLine":"　やはり余に不可能はないな","translatedEnglishLine":"there is indeed nothing impossible for me.\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: え、ちょ、ちょっと、やだ、ッ……！
俺、紳士やし、けっこう上手いで。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm a gentleman, and I'm pretty good at it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ちょっと……！　ラ、ランスっ……！」
縋るように、かなみがランスを見た。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami looked at Lance, clinging to him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うっひょっほーい！　お楽しみターイム！
チャンネルそのままやでー！」
わた、し、捨てられたの、っ……？
（ううん、最初っから……私なんて、遊び相手で……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (No, from the start... I was just a plaything...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あの時、ここでされた時と、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Compared to that time, when it happened here,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全然変わってなくて、っ……！）
俯いたかなみの目の奥で、涙が滲む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tears welled up deep in Kanami’s downcast eyes.
"Well then, straight to the event CG..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのかなみの腕をほくほく顔で悪魔が引こうとした、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just as the demon with a delighted face tried to pull Kanami's arm,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「なーーーーんて、嘘だばーーーか！！」
「うぅわぉぉっ！？　何すんねーーーん！」
いきなり斬りかかったランスに対し、
デーモンは慌てて腕でそれを打ち払った。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon hurriedly blocked it with his arm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「俺のものをくれてやるつもりなんぞ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "There was never any intention of giving you away,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私、ランスのもの、なんだ……まだ……

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Kanami, what are you spacing out for!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほな、すっ飛んでもらうで
異次元とゲートを繋ぐことができるなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you can connect an interdimensional gate,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その接続を切ることもまた可能
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: then severing that connection is also possible.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: やはり余に不可能はないな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: there is indeed nothing impossible for me."
